  • Packages that use Beta 
    Package Description
    co.cask.cdap.api.app
    An Application is a logical grouping of Streams, Datasets, Flows, Procedures, and other deployable elements.
    co.cask.cdap.api.data
    Defines means of integration between programs and data access.
    co.cask.cdap.api.data.batch
    Allows MapReduce jobs to read from and write to datasets.
    co.cask.cdap.api.data.format
    Defines data formats for use in programs and data exploration.
    co.cask.cdap.api.data.schema
    This package contains beta classes for schema in CDAP.
    co.cask.cdap.api.data.stream
    Stream specification and configuration.
    co.cask.cdap.api.dataset
    Defines APIs for accessing and managing data within CDAP.
    co.cask.cdap.api.dataset.lib
    Collection of Dataset implementations available out-of-the-box in CDAP.
    co.cask.cdap.api.dataset.metrics
    Defines integration points for Datasets and Metrics system.
    co.cask.cdap.api.dataset.module
    Defines deployment of custom Datasets to make them available within CDAP.
    co.cask.cdap.api.flow.flowlet
    Interfaces used in flows and flowlets.
    co.cask.cdap.api.metrics
    Defines a way to collect user-defined metrics.
